{"tha-ap450:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap450:0.2":"Vibhitakavagga ","tha-ap450:0.3":"Padapithiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap450:1.1":"“Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap450:1.2":"aggo karuniko muni; ","tha-ap450:1.3":"Tarayitva bahu satte, ","tha-ap450:1.4":"nibbuto so mahayaso. ","tha-ap450:2.1":"Sihasanassa samanta, ","tha-ap450:2.2":"sumedhassa mahesino; ","tha-ap450:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap450:2.4":"padapithamakarayim. ","tha-ap450:3.1":"Katvana kusalam kammam, ","tha-ap450:3.2":"sukhapakam sukhudrayam; ","tha-ap450:3.3":"Punnakammena samyutto, ","tha-ap450:3.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap450:4.1":"Tattha me vasamanassa, ","tha-ap450:4.2":"punnakammasamangino; ","tha-ap450:4.3":"Padani uddharantassa, ","tha-ap450:4.4":"sonnapitha bhavanti me. ","tha-ap450:5.1":"Labha tesam suladdham vo, ","tha-ap450:5.2":"ye labhanti upassutim; ","tha-ap450:5.3":"Nibbute karam katvana, ","tha-ap450:5.4":"labhanti vipulam sukham. ","tha-ap450:6.1":"Mayapi sukatam kammam, ","tha-ap450:6.2":"vanijjam suppayojitam; ","tha-ap450:6.3":"Padapitham karitvana, ","tha-ap450:6.4":"sonnapitham labhamaham. ","tha-ap450:7.1":"Yam yam disam pakkamami, ","tha-ap450:7.2":"kenaci kiccayenaham; ","tha-ap450:7.3":"Sonnapithe akkamami, ","tha-ap450:7.4":"punnakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap450:8.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap450:8.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap450:8.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap450:8.4":"padapithassidam phalam. ","tha-ap450:9.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap450:9.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap450:9.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap450:10.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap450:10.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap450:10.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap450:11.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap450:11.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap450:11.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap450:12.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma padapithiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap450:13.1":"Padapithiyattherassapadanam atthamam. "}